---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — Zac Culpan"
  description="Zac Culpan is a marketer, product person, and startup founder based in New Zealand. Writing about ecosystem marketing, creator marketing, and SaaS growth."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="post-header">
      <span class="post-tag">About</span>
      <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}zac-headshot-final.jpg`} alt="Zac Culpan" class="about-headshot" width="120" height="120" />
      <h1 class="post-title">Hi, I'm Zac.</h1>
      <p class="post-desc">Marketer, product person, and startup founder based in New Zealand.</p>
    </div>
    <article class="post-content">
      <p>I've been working in marketing and product for the better part of a decade now, mostly in SaaS. The through line across everything I've done is figuring out how companies grow, and specifically how they grow in ways that don't just rely on throwing more money at ads.</p>
      <p>Most recently I was Head of Marketing at <a href="https://www.narrative.so" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Narrative (opens in new tab)"><strong>Narrative</strong></a>, an AI-powered photo culling tool for professional photographers. That's where I got deep into ecosystem marketing, creator partnerships, and building a brand within a tight-knit professional community. I'm now Head of Product at <a href="https://www.oneroof.co.nz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="OneRoof (opens in new tab)"><strong>OneRoof</strong></a>, the real estate platform owned by NZME.</p>
      <p>Before that, I spent six months as a marketing contractor at <strong>Poliigon</strong>, working alongside BlenderGuru (one of the biggest 3D art creators on YouTube) to build out their marketing and growth strategy. Before that I was the first employee at <strong>BetterSaver</strong>, where I wore both the marketing and product hats and helped build the company from zero. And before that I was on the growth team at <strong>Vend</strong>, focused on organic growth and CRO.</p>
      <p>On the side, I'm co-founding a startup in the creator and influencer marketing measurement space. It's still early, but if you're interested in that world, you'll probably hear more about it here soon.</p>
      <h2>What I write about</h2>
      <p>This blog is where I share what I've learned and what I'm still figuring out. I write about ecosystem marketing, creator and influencer marketing measurement, SaaS growth strategy, and the stuff that sits between marketing and product. Everything here comes from real experience, not theory. If I haven't done it or seen it first-hand, I don't write about it.</p>
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Best place to reach me is <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zachary-culpan/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="LinkedIn (opens in new tab)">LinkedIn</a>. Always happy to chat.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>